<section class="setup-1">
  <article>
    <h1 class="hero-text-dark">Easy Setup</h1>
    <h5 class="hero-text-dark">ZokuVault is your virtual safety deposit box and estate planning portal. We help store your documents, relationships, and digital assets safely and securely.</h5>
  </article>
</section>

<section class="generic-dark">
  <article>
    <div class="cta-outer">
    <%= render :partial => 'pages/cta_short' %>
  </div>
    <h1>1. Sign Up</h1>
    <p>Break the inertia! Start small...  It is very easy to open an account with ZokuVault. So many people do not begin their estate plan or documentation process out of a feeling of overwhelming inertia. There is a fear of needing to complete everything at once.</p>
    <br><br>
  </article>
</section>

<section class="generic wall">


    <article class="get-help mw-20">
      <h1>Get Help</h1>
      <p>Ask your trusted professional advisers to assist in populating your ZokuVault.  If you work with Insurance Brokers, Financial Advisors, Trust and Estate Attorneys, Accountants, etc. as part of your risk management plan, ask them to assist you in populating your ZokuVault. It will be beneficial to both sides, and your Vault and Estate Plan will be closer to complete!</p>
    </article>


  <article>
    <h1>2. Enter Your Contacts</h1>
    <p>Just identifying the top 4 or 5 key contacts is 50% of the battle to most families. Get them into ZokuVault now and chip away over time. Before you know it, you will have your desired estate plan. Load in your important family memebers, accountants, attorneys, financial advisors and service providers.</p>
  </article>

  <article>
    <h1>3. Link Your Data</h1>
    <p>Upload key documents and link your online accounts.  ZokuVault makes it easy to store your:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Wills, Trusts, and Legal documents</li>
      <li>Financial Information</li>
      <li>Insurance Policies</li>
      <li>Tax Information</li>
      <li>Healthcare Choices</li>
      <li>Final Wishes</li>
      <li>Web Accounts</li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</section>

<section class="generic setup-2">

  <%= image_tag "marketing/files.png", :class => "fr mt-20" %>
  <article>
    <h1>4. Secure Sharing</h1>
    <p>Now that you have some information entered, make sure to get it into the hands of those that need to know.  We are confident that you have done a great job creating a plan, however, it is not as effective if you are the only person who knows where things are located or has access.  Share now, safely, securely and thoughtfully, so that your family is taken care of at the times that matter most.  Detail your plan in ZokuVault ,and share it at any level of depth with your most trusted family members and professional advisers before it is too late.</p>
    <br>
    <a class="button primary-button call-to-action" href="/mailing-list">Sign Up</a>
  </article>
</section>
